targets.queryText:
PRAGMA read_uncommitted = 1;
SELECT
   ReceiveTime,
   CPUStatAll as 'all',
   CPUStatUsr as 'usr',
   CPUStatSys as 'sys'
FROM 
   tkmSysProcStat  NOLOCK 
WHERE CPUStatName = 'cpu' AND ReceiveTime > ${__from:date:seconds} ORDER BY ReceiveTime;
